web.errors.why_is_this_secret_unavailabl.translation: Zakaj ta skrivnost ni na voljo?

web.errors.secrets_are_designed_to_be_vi.en: Secrets are designed to be viewed only once. This link may have already been accessed, expired, or been manually deleted by the sender.
web.errors.secrets_are_designed_to_be_vi.translation: Skrivnosti so zasnovane tako, da si jih je mogoče ogledati samo enkrat. Ta povezava je morda že bila dostopana, je potekla ali jo je pošiljatelj ročno izbrisal.

web.errors.contact_the_person_who_sent_y.en: Contact the person who sent you this link and ask them to create a new secret. Let them know you weren't able to access the original information.
web.errors.contact_the_person_who_sent_y.translation: Kontaktirajte osebo, ki vam je poslala to povezavo, in jo prosite, naj ustvari novo skrivnost. Povejte ji, da niste mogli dostopati do izvirnih informacij.

web.errors.oops_the_page_you_are_looking.en: Oops! The page you are looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.
web.errors.oops_the_page_you_are_looking.translation: Ups! Stran, ki jo iščete, ne obstaja ali je bila premaknjena.

web.errors.if_youre_unsure_what_to_do_ne.en: If you're unsure what to do next, please follow up with the person who sent you this link for more information.
web.errors.if_youre_unsure_what_to_do_ne.translation: Če niste prepričani, kaj storiti naprej, se prosimo obrnite na osebo, ki vam je poslala to povezavo za več informacij.

web.errors.information_shared_through_ou.en: Information shared through our service can only be accessed once. Once viewed, the content is permanently deleted from our servers to ensure confidentiality. This approach helps protect your sensitive data by limiting its exposure and preventing unauthorized access.
web.errors.information_shared_through_ou.translation: Informacije, deljene preko naše storitve, je mogoče dostopati samo enkrat. Ko so ogledane, je vsebina trajno izbrisana z naših strežnikov za zagotovitev zaupnosti. Ta pristop pomaga zaščititi vaše občutljive podatke z omejevanjem njihove izpostavljenosti in preprečevanjem nepooblaščenega dostopa.

web.errors.were_sorry_but_an_unexpected_.en: We're sorry, but an unexpected error occurred while processing your request. Our team has been notified and we're working to fix it.
web.errors.were_sorry_but_an_unexpected_.translation: Opravičujemo se, vendar je prišlo do nepričakovane napake med obdelavo vaše zahteve. Naša ekipa je bila obveščena in delamo na odpravi težave.

web.errors.the_page_youre_looking_for_do.en: The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved. Don't worry, it happens to the best of us!
web.errors.the_page_youre_looking_for_do.translation: Stran, ki jo iščete, ne obstaja ali je bila premaknjena. Ne skrbite, to se zgodi najboljšim!

web.errors.unable_to_load_data_due_to_da.en: Unable to load data due to data format issues. Please try again later.
web.errors.unable_to_load_data_due_to_da.translation: Ni mogoče naložiti podatkov zaradi težav s formatom podatkov. Poskusite znova kasneje.
